{"tid":2282314,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"扎醒就諗起社會啲嘢好辛苦","createTime":"2020-11-11T19:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T20:20:29.000Z","uid":367597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0261c0d2e9882446f3c0d5dc4c9c99d2f622ab20","tid":2282314,"uid":367597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T19:38:10.000Z","msg":"啱啱發噩夢嚇撚醒咗，然後一上連登就睇咗幾個關於理大嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又忍唔住係咁喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解我依家仲可以高床軟枕而人哋就流亡海外<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我到底有咩用，點解我唔可以勇敢啲做多少少嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢排大壓力情緒真係唔係幾好，自己又唔識控制，去親有發生過事嘅地方就會諗起嗰陣嘅發生嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後又諗起幾多人依家受緊苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我仲可以如常生活真係好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解做個有良知嘅人會係一件咁辛苦嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時候真係忍唔住羨慕嗰啲乜都唔知嘅港豬，佢哋仲可以好似冇事發生咁繼續開開心心地生活真係好，但我哋已經翻唔到轉頭去翻呢啲日子㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5e4507dd3a7fe9e00e5191aed2e17cce59123e","tid":2282314,"uid":367597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T19:38:56.000Z","msg":"我都知我有咁嘅諗法都係因為我自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e669f794bfcf41272917edb546763e3e43afd4b","tid":2282314,"uid":367597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T19:41:56.000Z","msg":"依家喊到攰又唔敢瞓驚再發噩夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40097cdd0f51e58bc069ebcd4032fe3323791c19","tid":2282314,"uid":258345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T19:48:00.000Z","msg":"有時都好suprise 係我地老師教錯哂我地.<br />\n或者冇良知, 冇是非黑白, 點去考慮點去食玩訓, 生存, 交配, 應該好好多.<br />\n<br />\n幸福可以好簡單, 唔好做&quot;人&quot;就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/so